items.title: “I’m a typical dribbler, I like to attack,”
"This is more than a humanitarian mission. It is an act of moral resistance against the silence of the world,"

“La fase di tempo più stabile e soleggiato sarà accompagnata da un nuovo rialzo delle temperature - (\*) - . Entro il prossimo weekend le massime si porteranno vicine ai 28-30°C al Centro-Nord, con picchi locali anche di 31-32°C su Emilia-Romagna e interne tirreniche. Al Sud, specie nel fine settimana e all’inizio della prossima, il caldo tornerà a farsi sentire in particolar modo su Isole maggiori, basso Adriatico e settori ionici, con picchi locali anche di 34-36°C”

“Prior to the incident, Mayor Giuliani was flagged down by a woman who was the victim of a domestic violence incident. Mayor Giuliani immediately rendered assistance and contacted 911,” “He remained on scene until responding officers arrived to ensure her safety. Following this, while traveling on the highway, Mayor Giuliani’s vehicle was struck from behind at high speed”
